      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**The Recording_delay column is crucial for assessing data quality and operational transparency:**\n",
        "\n",
        "Positive Delays (Recording is late): This is the primary concern, as it means the system's tracking is not reflecting real-time inventory and delivery status. If a client calls about a shipment, the system status is unreliable.\n",
        "\n",
        "Negative Delays (Recording is early): This usually indicates data errors or an administrative policy of marking a shipment as \"delivered\" once it leaves the last distribution center, rather than when the client physically receives it."
