        "### Logistical Strategy Implication\n",
        "The analysis advocates for a **stratified logistics strategy**:\n",
        "1.  **Cost Leader:** **Maximize Ocean** for all feasible bulk procurement.\n",
        "2.  **Service/Reliability:** **Use Air Charter** for high-volume, critical shipments (like ARV surges) to gain significant economies of scale and avoid the high relative cost of standard air freight.\n",
